---
// About section - Botanical brand design
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-[#F5F5F0]">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">

      <!-- Image with decorative border offset -->
      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Sage green decorative border (offset behind image) -->
        <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 right-0 bottom-0 border-2 border-[#5D6B5D] -z-10"></div>

        <!-- Main image -->
        <img
          src="/images/hero-interior.jpg"
          alt="The Loft Bar interior with living green wall and elegant seating"
          class="aspect-[4/5] w-full object-cover"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Text Content -->
      <div>
        <!-- Section Label -->
        <span class="text-[#5D6B5D] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-sm mb-4 block">
          Our Story
        </span>

        <!-- Heading -->
        <h2 class="font-sans text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-[#2A2A2A] mb-8 leading-tight tracking-[0.1em] uppercase font-light">
          Welcome to The Loft
        </h2>

        <!-- Description -->
        <div class="space-y-6 text-[#4A4A4A] text-lg leading-relaxed font-light">
          <p>
            Perched above the historic waterways of the River Don, The Loft offers
            a botanical escape in the heart of Kelham Island. Step inside and discover
            a space where nature and elegance intertwine.
          </p>

          <p>
            Our living green wall cascades with verdant foliage, while delicate
            wisteria trails from the original oak beams overhead. Sink into plush
            velvet seating as dappled light filters through the leaves, creating
            an atmosphere of refined tranquillity.
          </p>

          <p>
            Whether you're here for expertly crafted cocktails, intimate conversation,
            or simply to escape the everyday, The Loft provides a sanctuary unlike
            anywhere else in Sheffield.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Private Hire CTA -->
        <div class="mt-10 pt-8 border-t border-[#5D6B5D]/20">
          <p class="text-[#4A4A4A] font-light mb-4">
            Looking for a unique venue for your next event? The Loft is available
            for private hire.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://www.instagram.com/loftkelham"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center text-[#5D6B5D] hover:text-[#4A5A4A] transition-colors font-medium"
          >
            <span>DM us on Instagram to enquire</span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
